### Design
- Inherits from TV9 (best tournament base)
- Only overrides _explore_action for agent 0 aligner when team >= 5
- Agent 0 cycles through 32 full-map waypoints (r15-r38) during idle explore
- Other agents use standard r22 offsets
- Gate: team_size >= 5 (small teams use standard TV9 behavior)

